# This directory contains user settings saved as individual JSON files
# Files in this directory:
# - mode.json - Current mode (roleplay/normal)
# - roleplay.json - Roleplay mode settings (world, characters)
# - utility.json - Utility mode settings (assistant identity, guardrails)
# - userPersona.json - User persona and preferences
# - general.json - General settings (model, temperature, etc.)
# - meta.json - Metadata (template ID, last modified, version)
